nodes.text: Mytaranor was a planet located in the Mytaranor sector of the Mid Rim region of the galaxy. A lackluster industrial world, Mytaranor was known for being inhabited by many slavers (the most prominent being the Mytaranor Slaving Council) who specialized in the trade of Wookiee slaves from the neighboring Kashyyyk system.
Despite sharing its name with the sector, it was not the sector capital, as custom would suggest. Instead, Randon occupied this position.
